604
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:12,970
Of course.

605
00:39:13,940 --> 00:39:17,210
The Celestial Crane City is the hub of the southeast.

606
00:39:18,950 --> 00:39:19,760
Understood.

607
00:39:20,070 --> 00:39:20,970
Which means

608
00:39:21,550 --> 00:39:24,650
many from the Celestial Palace

609
00:39:24,990 --> 00:39:26,470
