610
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:29,240
I'll give orders immediately.

611
00:39:29,900 --> 00:39:30,970
We'll move out tomorrow.

612
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:33,360
In full force.

613
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,130
Absolutely.

614
00:39:35,780 --> 00:39:37,360
