618
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:47,360
Perhaps she got held up.

619
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:49,360
If she still doesn't appear,

620
00:39:50,860 --> 00:39:53,130
I'll kick You Chi from his throne

621
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:56,880
