625
00:40:20,460 --> 00:40:21,800
That's incredible!

626
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:23,880
I knew I followed the right person.

627
00:40:27,740 --> 00:40:31,610
I've long heard the fame of Winter City Lord and Lord of Mercy.

628
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:35,800
Since you rule the Demon Realm,

629
00:40:35,990 --> 00:40:39,210
